==English==

===Etymology===
[[alpha]] ''(the first letter of the Greek alphabet)'' + [[-gram]] ''(something written or drawn)''

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The [[letter]]s of a [[word]], or any other set of letters, arranged into [[alphabetical]] order.
#*''The alphagram of the word <code>ALPHABETICAL</code> is <code>AAABCEHILLPT</code>.''

